00:10:35.660 --> 00:10:39.540
Well, at the point we were the largest hotelier
in the Bay Area, we had no hotels outside

00:10:39.540 --> 00:10:41.839
the Bay Area so we were in a lot of trouble.

00:10:41.839 --> 00:10:46.439
