dish.

00:49:06.920 --> 00:49:11.000
We learned from Daniel Goleman 16 years ago
when he wrote the book Emotional Intelligence

00:49:11.000 --> 00:49:15.759
that two-thirds of the success of business
leaders tended to come from their emotional

00:49:15.759 --> 00:49:21.819
intelligence, their EQ, and about a third,
on average, from their IQ and from their level

00:49:21.819 --> 00:49:23.519
