00:49:23.519 --> 00:49:27.369
So it was the first sort of, there was work
done before Daniel Goleman ever wrote about

00:49:27.369 --> 00:49:28.940
this, but this is where it got popularized.

00:49:28.940 --> 00:49:31.859
So 16 years later we know this.

00:49:31.859 --> 00:49:38.140
Smart guy here in a different state right
there.

00:49:38.140 --> 00:49:45.260
