and he's proven the following: when you're

00:49:45.260 --> 00:49:51.920
feeling anxious or angry or frustrated, when
you make decisions from that place of anger

00:49:51.920 --> 00:49:59.890
or anxiety and you try to make a decision
in that moment, you're losing 10 to 15 IQ

00:49:59.890 --> 00:50:02.910
points in the act of making that decision.

00:50:02.910 --> 00:50:07.079
Now if I'm giving a speech to a non-Google
crowd I would say the following: "Some of

00:50:07.079 --> 00:50:09.950
